data.title: 以 3 到 5 分钟描写以下主题
data.content: Describe a time when you had to work very hard to achieve a goal. What did you learn from the experience?
data.answer: When I was in high school, I signed in a school sports competition, and in order to achieve good results, I decided to run five kilometers  every day for over one month to train myself. The training worked and I eventually won first place and brought honor to my class. I learned from this that we need to pursue our goals bravely and if we try our best and challenge ourselves, we will definitely be rewarded and we will learn from the experience.
